OL,3,CTrains cancelled and schools close as
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heat predicted
OL,6,FTemperatures could soar as high as 36C
OL,7,Fin parts of south Wales.
OL,9,FTrain passengers are being urged to
OL,10,Fonly travel if "absolutely necessary"
OL,11,Fon Thursday and Friday due to the
OL,12,Fextreme heat, with many services
OL,13,Fcancelled too.
OL,15,FNetwork Rail said trains will operate
OL,16,Fat reduced speeds and services will be
OL,17,Fcut for "safety reasons".
