OL,3,CTrains cancelled and schools close as
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heat predicted
OL,6,FHeat-related issues that can affect
OL,7,Fthe railway include buckled rails,
OL,8,Fsagging overhead electric wires and
OL,9,Flineside fires. Steel rails can exceed
OL,10,F50C when the air temperature is 30C.
OL,12,FTransport for Wales have cancelled
OL,13,Fseveral routes, including between
OL,14,FMaesteg and Bridgend and Chester and
OL,15,FWrexham, until late Thursday night and
OL,16,Fwarned that other services may also be
OL,17,Fimpacted.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
