OL,3,CTrains cancelled and schools close as
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heat predicted
OL,6,FThe company advised people to check
OL,7,Fbefore the travel, allow extra time
OL,8,Ffor their journey and bring water with
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FThe number of school closures in Wales
OL,12,Fcontinues to rise with more than 800
OL,13,Fschools shut due to the extreme heat.
OL,15,FSchools in Powys, Carmarthenshire and
OL,16,FCeredigion have seen an increased
OL,17,Fnumber of closures for Thursday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
