OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782384482
OL,3,CTrains cancelled and schools close as
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heat predicted
OL,6,FIt comes as a 50-year-old man has died
OL,7,Fafter entering the water during the
OL,8,Fextreme heat at Aberavon beach.
OL,9,FEmergency services attended the beach
OL,10,Fon Wednesday (24 June) afternoon but
OL,11,Fthe man was pronounced dead at the
OL,12,Fscene.
